quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  55,46,"wlmn atqa allah min eibadih min al'iins waljn, fkhaf mqamh bayn ydyh, fataeh, wtrk measyh, jntan"
  55,47,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,48,aljntan dhawata aghsan nadratan min alfwakh walthmar
  55,49,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,50,fy hatayn aljanatayn eaynan min alma' tajrian khlalhma
  55,51,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,52,fy hatayn aljanatayn min kuli nawe min alfwakh snfan
  55,53,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,54,"wlldhyn khafuu maqam rabihim janatan ytnemwn fyhma, mutakiiyn ealaa furush mbttant min ghaliz aldybaj, wthmr aljanatayn qarib 'ilyhm"
  55,55,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,56,"fy hadhih alfrsh zwjat qasirat 'absarihina ealaa azwajhn, la ynzrn 'iilaa ghyrhm mtelqat bhm, lm ytahn 'iins qablahum wala jan"
  55,57,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,58,kan hwla' alzwjat min alhwr alyaqwt walmarjan fi sfayhn wjmalhn
  55,59,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,60,hal jaza' man 'ahsan bemlh fi aldunya 'iilaa al'iihsan 'iilayh bialjanat fi alakhr? fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,61,hl jaza' man 'ahsan bemlh fi aldunya 'iilaa al'iihsan 'iilayh bialjanat fi alakhr? fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,62,wmn dun aljanatayn alssabiqatayn janatan akhryan. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,63,wmn dun aljanatayn alssabiqatayn janatan akhryan. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,64,"hatan aljntan khdrawan, qad ashtddat khdrthma hataa malt 'iilaa alswad. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?"
  55,65,"hatan aljntan khdrawan, qad ashtddat khdrthma hataa malt 'iilaa alswad. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?"
  55,66,fyhma eaynan fwwartan bialma' la tnqtean. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,67,fyhma eaynan fwwartan bialma' la tnqtean. fabi'ayi nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,68,fy hatayn aljanatayn 'anwae alfwakh wanakhl wrman
  55,69,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,70,fy hadhih aljnan al'arbae zwjat tayibat al'akhlaq hisan alwjwh
  55,71,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,72,hwr mstwrat mswnat fi alkhyam
  55,73,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,74,lm yta hwla' alhwr 'iins qabl 'azwajahuna wala jan
  55,75,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,76,mtkyyn ealaa wsayd dhwat aghtyt khadir wafurush hsan
  55,77,fbay nieam rabukuma -ayha althqlan- tkdhdhiban?
  55,78,"tkathrt brkt asm rabik wkthr khyrh, dhi aljalal albahr, walmjd alkaml, wal'iikram lawlyayh"